1) Prepare a simulation and reconstruction ROOT file. You can use config files 
	Config/SimulateElastic_*.cfg in CVS offline/user/jan
to simulate elastic events. Then perform elastic reconstruction using file (don't forget to enter the input/output files etc.)
	Config/ReconstructElastic.cfg in CVS offline/user/jan

2) Update data/validation.cfg: enter your input and output file. Select whether to compare reconstructed quantities to smeared or unsmeared MC values

3) cmsRun data/validation.cfg

4) View results using ROOT.
#or the script following root -l scripts/showResults.cc
